{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji36","name":"毛泽东全集第36卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji36.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给许志行的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给许志行的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1956年1月26日）志行兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月八日惠书早已收到，甚为感激，迟复为歉。现在是寒假，如果你愿意，可以来北京一叙（到中南海找叶子龙\"）。暑假可去韶山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年一月廿六日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]许志行，1919年冬在武汉和毛泽东相识，1926年曾应毛泽东之邀到广州国民党中央宣传部工作。当时在上海格致中学教书。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]叶子龙，当时任毛泽东的秘书。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":1,"day":26}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":196,"page_end":196},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}